snippet.title: ATV Renegades - Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/atv-renegades-ps4/

The video showcases both the racing and tricks you can do in ATV Renegades.  It shows off both single and multiplayer and has the players racing in multiple environments acroos various continents.  It also shows various crashes that players could have if they do not execute thir tricks correctly.

http://www.nighthawkinteractive.com
